Privacy Policy for OffGrid Survival
Effective Date: 09/04/25

OffGrid Survival does not collect any personal data and only utilizes the standard encryption provided by Apple's iOS frameworks (for example, MCSession with encryptionPreference set to .required).

Data Collection
The app does not collect any personal or personally identifiable information.

Crash data is automatically gathered by Apple’s systems in the event of a crash to help improve system stability.

Data Usage
All collected data is used solely for enhancing the app’s functionality and stability.

No user data is shared with third parties.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
Any changes to this Privacy Policy will be posted on this page. We encourage you to review the policy periodically.

Contact
If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us via the App Store.
